metadata.name: rilles tape club (vol. 2) 1/50
metadata.description: hey there, and welcome to rilles tape club! my name is rilles, and i make music. you can think of this rilles tape club NFT as a friendship bracelet that i made for your digital wrist :). the NFT will get you access to a token-gated channel in my discord server, where you can hear music before it's released along with stuff in progress. the NFT is free because my aim is to make connections with people in the web3 community who like my music (or who dislike my music but otherwise want to support me, lol). please don't ask me about other utility... from my perspective, the music and the community are utility enough. <3
